.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^x%^RESET%^ - the real x coordinate
%^BOLD%^y%^RESET%^ - the real y coordinate
%^BOLD%^moves_left%^RESET%^ - the number of moves left to pop along
%^BOLD%^jump%^RESET%^ - the jump length we are looking for
%^BOLD%^main_key%^RESET%^ - the key, this is only used for non-road jumps
